{"tid":1534321,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"劉小麗倘上訴成功 陳凱欣勢出局","createTime":"2019-09-03T03:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T03:28:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"07ba3c66758c7e44c5b6174165f99e874f808f4b","tid":1534321,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:23:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190903/20761120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190903%2F20761120&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=d0cc8d4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190903%2F20761120&h=abe3b1a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190903/20761120</a><br />\n<br />\n劉小麗倘上訴成功 陳凱欣勢出局<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190903/large/1567442699_1ff2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190903%2Flarge%2F1567442699_1ff2.jpg&h=3f3e248f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉小麗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】高院昨日裁定香港眾志常委周庭的選舉呈請勝訴，除周庭外，多名被DQ的民主派人士亦有就其參選資格提出呈請，前議員劉小麗向《蘋果》表示，她和律師團隊會參考周庭案的判詞，再審視選舉呈請的內容，希望法庭可澄清選舉主任權力範圍，社民連梁國雄則指，無論周庭案的結果如何，都會上訴到終院。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：周庭︰自決係港人最基本權利<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190903/large/1567442698_43ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190903%2Flarge%2F1567442698_43ea.jpg&h=2ee6d4a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳凱欣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁國雄研上訴至終院<br />\n<br />\n劉小麗去年11月報名參與立法會九龍西補選，選舉主任當時以劉小麗主張自決為由，指她非真誠擁護《基本法》，裁定她提名無效。劉在今年初就此提出選舉呈請，案件仍在排期中。劉小麗指不便透露案件詳情，但會參考周庭案判詞再審視選舉呈請內容，暫未評估勝算，但指選舉主任在其案中做法比周庭案更粗暴「問都無問就DQ我」。若劉小麗上訴成功，勝出九西補選建制派陳凱欣可能失去議席，陳透過助理回應《蘋果》查詢，尊重法庭判決，至於其他正進行呈請個案不便評論。<br />\n<br />\n至於同樣因宣誓無效被撤銷議員資格的梁國雄指，正繼續研究上訴至終院的可行性，但認為周庭案裁決，只進一步確立選舉主任有權判斷參選人是否真誠擁護《基本法》，他又指無論周庭案的判決結果如何，都會繼續上訴至終院。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n區諾軒促選舉主任辭職<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n四人疑用「滅魔棍」虐殺21歲女<br />\n<br />\n周庭︰自決係港人最基本權利<br />\n區諾軒促選舉主任辭職<br />\n「選舉主任有權審核候選人政見」官︰DQ前失解釋權 選舉呈請 周庭慘勝"},{"pid":"ffc3909aec78d69eddadc402faccb7a00f0bfcc8","tid":1534321,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:25:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa4a4bab774e92beceb870a1b3f66a1dc0ca70ed","tid":1534321,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:27:27.000Z","msg":"你今次仲唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf26fd75cb271e4cdf73b4eaf596d02a97d492f","tid":1534321,"uid":35746,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:27:55.000Z","msg":"再選 都冇人會投小麗，長毛<br />\n做唔到野，比人dq風險又大<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過都希望上訴成功"},{"pid":"f2a731a19e2eb79924e50e7844787b36d0e0a169","tid":1534321,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:28:55.000Z","msg":"毛哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}